    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it! It\u2019s in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and it still has that 'new car' magic. It drives like a total dream! If you're looking for something flawless and ready to hit the road, this is definitely the one. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
