    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3, featuring the naturally aspirated S54 3.2L inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a full VANOS overhaul and structural subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The engine exhibits zero oil seepage at the rear main seal, and the valvetrain remains exceptionally quiet. This is a mechanically pristine, turn-key investment for the discerning driver who values engineering integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
