    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a showroom-quality masterpiece that defies its age. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, appearing exactly as it did on the delivery floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks or rock chips, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple without a single crease, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma, having never been smoked in or exposed to pets. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, featuring a documented history of preventative maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. Every button, sensor, and feature operates with tactile precision. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing no signs of road salt or inclement weather use, and the wheels are free of any curb rash, wrapped in fresh, high-performance rubber. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously preserved investment for a buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
