    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are privileged to present this exceptional motorcar, maintained in impeccable, showroom condition. This vehicle exhibits a level of preservation that is truly rare, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in a state of absolute refinement. Every detail reflects a commitment to excellence, offering an unrivaled opportunity for the discerning driver who demands nothing less than perfection. This is, without compromise, a benchmark example of its model.",
