    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 1997 Porsche 911 (993) Carrera. This final-year air-cooled specimen features the 3.6L M64 flat-six equipped with the Varioram induction system, delivering linear power through a precise G50 six-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains exceptionally taut, utilizing the LSA multi-link rear suspension for unparalleled lateral stability and kinematics. Mechanically flawless, the crankcase shows zero oil seepage, with original factory cosmoline still preserved on the undercarriage. All systems\u2014from the Bosch Motronic engine management to the four-piston Brembo-sourced calipers\u2014operate at peak performance parameters. This is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist demanding mechanical perfection.",
